com.fluidops.iwb.cms
Interface File

All Known Implementing Classes:
ArchiveFile, FileBase, LocalFile, ReadOnlyFile, WebDirectory, WebFile
public interface File

interface to abstract away diffent types of File storage 1) java.io.File 2) NFS 3) WebDav 4) Amazon S3 5) EMC Atmos 6) Google Docs ...

aeb
